## 3) `CHANGELOG.md`

```md
# Changelog

## v1.0.0
- Initial public release
- Export Exchange Online Accepted Domains to CSV
- Optional DNS checks (MX via Resolve-DnsName, SPF/DKIM/DMARC/MTA via DomainHealthChecker)
- Best-effort ARC config inclusion (Get-ArcConfig)
- Robust error handling and PS7 compatibility